org.pepstock.charba.client.impl.plugins

Class SelectionCleaner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.impl.plugins.SelectionCleaner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IsDatasetsItemsSelectorDefaultSelectionCleaner

    public final class SelectionCleaner
extends NativeObjectContainer
implements IsDatasetsItemsSelectorDefaultSelectionCleaner
    DatasetsItemsSelector.ID plugin configuration element in order to have in the the chart a clickable element to clear the selection.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
